          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Responsible Skies Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Amends the FAA Modernization and Reform Act of 2012 to require the Secretary of Transportation to prohibit the operator of an unmanned recreational aircraft (drone) from flying it:</p> <ul> <li>above 400 feet and within 5 miles of the perimeter of a commercial airport, or</li> <li>where it may be seen from the airport's perimeter.</li> </ul>]]></text>
